metadata.name: Jostedalsbreen, Briksdsle Gacier
metadata.description:
Amazing experience in this glacier where we witnessed the detachment of a huge sheet of ice. 

Unfortunately the glacier is retreating more and more and I can say that I have witnessed it.

 How long will these majestic beauties last?

Poetic stands out against the sky,  glacial and imposing reminds us that we are on this earth guests of a greater god: Mother Nature
